- Add netlify/functions/send-welcome.js: sends branded welcome email with
  login credentials (email address, login URL, plan, trial end date) after
  every new account is created — works for both email/password and Google auth

- onboarding.html: call send-welcome after Firebase account creation for
  all sign-up paths; change trial period from 14 to 15 days

- index.html: replace vague hero CTA with clear 3-step flow (sign up →
  15-day free trial → choose plan); update nav to show "Start Free Trial"
  prominently alongside Sign In; fix all "14 days" copy to "15 days"

- signin.html, starter.html, growth.html, premium.html: update "14-day
  free trial" to "15-day free trial" in paywall and sign-up link copy

